♪I thought I had no time to be timid♪

309
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:57,470
♪If we surrender♪

310
00:18:57,490 --> 00:18:59,410
You shouldn’t have taken the pills.

311
00:18:59,410 --> 00:19:04,510
♪Can we stop hating♪

312
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:07,210
Give this whisk

313
00:19:07,210 --> 00:19:09,580
to Li Sheng.

314
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:13,460
Maybe the thing behind it

315
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,940
can save you.

316
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:18,600
♪In no fear of strong wine♪

317
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:19,970
♪I cover my face♪

318
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:23,300
Whatever you want me to do,

319
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:24,880
I won’t do it.

320
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:27,670
♪Break down last wishes♪

321
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:29,040
♪I Have to♪

322
00:19:29,050 --> 00:19:33,660
Take no more Phoenix Pills!

323
00:19:33,660 --> 00:19:36,060
Two years!

324
00:19:36,060 --> 00:19:36,850
Two...

325
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:38,110
♪Forever♪

326
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:39,440
♪I thought I had no time to be timid♪

327
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,100
Two...

328
