♪If we surrender♪

329
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:46,070
♪Can we stop hating♪

330
00:19:46,090 --> 00:19:48,250
Two years, fine.

331
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:50,480
I will choose

332
00:19:52,730 --> 00:19:54,080
my own fate.

333
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:23,370
Who are you?

334
00:20:23,370 --> 00:20:25,420
I’m known

335
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,900
as Black Judge.

336
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:29,300
Why don’t you be White Reaper

337
00:20:29,300 --> 00:20:30,940
and my apprentice?

338
00:20:30,940 --> 00:20:34,370
Say it again!

339
00:20:34,370 --> 00:20:36,890
You have good martial arts.

340
00:20:38,330 --> 00:20:41,300
Why does Chongxiao always protect you?

341
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:43,580
What do you mean by protecting me?

342
00:20:43,580 --> 00:20:45,460
I ran after him all the way here.

343
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:47,210
He took my whisk

344
00:20:47,210 --> 00:20:48,850
and hid in the mountains.

345
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:51,490
Finally, he went down the mountain

346
00:20:51,490 --> 00:20:53,090
and visited the blacksmith’s shop

347
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:54,850
to forge scabbards.

348
00:20:54,850 --> 00:20:56,780
He forged a dozen scabbards.

349
00:20:58,250 --> 00:20:59,850
He’s the chief of Qi School.

350
00:20:59,850 --> 00:21:02,460
But he did such a stupid thing

351
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:04,580
just for a young man.

352
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:06,010
Isn’t it funny?

353
00:21:13,730 --> 00:21:14,900
Psychopath!

354
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:21,700
You killed him?

355
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:31,210
I did.

356
00:21:32,970 --> 00:21:36,130
I punched him and he died.

357
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:46,900
(Lingling)

358
00:22:19,730 --> 00:22:21,130
Young Master.

359
00:22:21,130 --> 00:22:22,610
My Lady.

360
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:23,940
When we’re in Lingling Town,

361
00:22:23,940 --> 00:22:25,490
we’re within the territory
of the Huo family.

362
00:22:25,490 --> 00:22:27,060
At the Demon-Extermination Assembly
in a few days,

363
00:22:27,060 --> 00:22:29,090
you must be very cautious
with your words and actions.

364
00:22:29,090 --> 00:22:31,300
Don’t offend Junior Master Huo.

365
00:22:31,300 --> 00:22:32,700
Don’t worry, Mr. Lin.

366
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:34,420
I hear everybody else goes there,

367
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:36,660
for the ripple pattern.

368
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:38,660
(Zhu Chen, Xingnan Sect)
We’re not interested in that.

369
00:22:38,660 --> 00:22:40,420
We’ll be fine.

370
00:22:40,420 --> 00:22:41,700
Brother.

371
00:22:41,700 --> 00:22:43,610
Then why did you leave
all business behind

372
00:22:43,610 --> 00:22:45,540
and come here
after receiving the invitation?

373
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:47,210
(Zhu Ying, Xingnan Sect)
We don’t have great martial arts.

374
00:22:47,210 --> 00:22:49,610
(Zhu Ying, Xingnan Sect)
We can’t help much to fight the Demons.

375
00:22:49,610 --> 00:22:51,250
Why must we come?

376
00:22:51,250 --> 00:22:52,940
Ying, don’t talk nonsense.

377
00:22:53,210 --> 00:22:56,010
Old Master Huo’s been nice to us.

378
00:22:56,010 --> 00:22:57,180
Thanks to them,

379
00:22:57,180 --> 00:22:59,580
we have no problem
doing business in the south.

380
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:01,180
We received the invitation.

381
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:01,940
Anyway,

382
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:04,090
we should come
and support Junior Master Huo.

383
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:15,970
What are you looking at?

384
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,900
It’s summer.

385
00:23:28,900 --> 00:23:30,820
But that man is shivering with cold.

386
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:32,180
Is he sick?

387
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:33,610
Ying, go.

388
00:23:33,610 --> 00:23:35,490
Take out a robe from our luggage

389
00:23:35,490 --> 00:23:37,130
and give it to that man.

390
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:39,060
You’re trying to help people again.

391
00:23:50,700 --> 00:23:52,010
My brother asked me to give this to you.

392
00:23:58,610 --> 00:23:59,540
Thank you.

393
00:24:02,130 --> 00:24:02,850
Thank you.

394
00:24:02,850 --> 00:24:03,900
You’re welcome.

395
00:24:23,940 --> 00:24:29,660
(Lingling Inn)

396
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:44,700
Why are the coins so cold?

397
00:24:45,210 --> 00:24:46,890
What are you doing? Robbing?

398
00:24:47,140 --> 00:24:49,420
(Animal characters made by CG)

399
00:24:51,250 --> 00:24:51,830
Go back.

400
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:52,660
(Animal characters made by CG)

401
00:24:55,620 --> 00:25:02,220
(Lingling Inn)

402
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:19,580
(Poisoner Ying Hecong)

403
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:29,060
(Lingling Inn)

404
00:25:45,490 --> 00:25:47,060
Miss, how many of you are there?

405
00:25:47,060 --> 00:25:48,010
Just me.

406
00:25:48,010 --> 00:25:49,300
Come in, please.

407
00:25:49,300 --> 00:25:51,010
Come on. This way, please.

408
00:26:18,130 --> 00:26:19,180
Come in, please.

409
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:20,300
Young Master.

410
00:26:20,300 --> 00:26:21,820
That girl killed people before.

411
00:26:21,820 --> 00:26:23,010
Don’t stare at her.

412
00:26:29,060 --> 00:26:31,460
Miss, are you with Cloud Ravine?

413
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:35,090
I’m with Blue Bat.

414
00:26:35,090 --> 00:26:36,490
You’re just in time.

415
00:26:36,490 --> 00:26:37,820
There was a customer,

416
00:26:37,820 --> 00:26:40,330
looking like the man you’re after.

417
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:42,180
He left the coins.

418
00:26:45,610 --> 00:26:47,610
They’re not special.

419
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:49,300
But when he gave them to me,

420
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:50,700
they were cold as ice.

421
00:26:54,970 --> 00:26:56,370
Where has he gone?

422
00:26:56,370 --> 00:26:57,580
I’m sorry,

423
00:26:57,580 --> 00:26:59,420
but I don’t know.

424
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:00,900
These days, people come and go

425
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:03,330
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

426
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:06,370
I’m afraid you can’t catch up with him.

427
00:27:06,370 --> 00:27:08,090
But since he’s in town,

428
00:27:08,090 --> 00:27:10,540
he needs accommodation and traffic.

429
00:27:10,540 --> 00:27:13,660
Our business covers half of
the basic needs.

430
00:27:13,660 --> 00:27:15,090
The man you’re after...

431
00:27:15,090 --> 00:27:17,540
He could be negligent,
however careful he is.

432
00:27:17,540 --> 00:27:20,130
Why don’t you stay in our inn

433
00:27:20,130 --> 00:27:21,490
and wait for more news?

434
00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:23,850
Fine.

435
00:27:24,330 --> 00:27:25,370
Thanks, then.

436
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:31,820
Isn’t he supposed

437
00:27:31,820 --> 00:27:34,460
to be in the south for sunlight?

438
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:38,210
Why did he come here?

439
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:49,400
Let’s sit there.

440
00:27:50,060 --> 00:27:50,850
Waiter...

441
00:27:59,940 --> 00:28:01,130
Get up. Get up.

442
00:28:01,130 --> 00:28:03,250
I don’t like the food in this inn.

443
00:28:03,250 --> 00:28:04,460
You tried any before?

444
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:06,060
I don’t like it.
Let’s try another restaurant.

445
00:28:06,060 --> 00:28:08,300
Miss, our food tastes good.

446
00:28:08,300 --> 00:28:09,460
Shut up!

447
00:28:11,370 --> 00:28:13,130
I... I mean...

448
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:14,330
We’ll discuss about it

449
00:28:14,330 --> 00:28:16,090
and order the dishes later.

450
00:28:16,090 --> 00:28:17,210
Fine. Fine.

451
00:28:19,010 --> 00:28:20,010
Sit down.

452
00:28:26,300 --> 00:28:27,210
Who?

453
00:28:27,210 --> 00:28:28,060
No one.

454
00:28:33,610 --> 00:28:34,970
Zhou Fei!

455
00:28:36,090 --> 00:28:36,940
What are you doing?

456
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:38,130
What are you doing?

457
00:28:38,130 --> 00:28:39,820
I want to challenge her.

458
00:28:39,820 --> 00:28:41,130
We come for
the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

459
00:28:41,130 --> 00:28:42,130
If you challenge her,

460
00:28:42,130 --> 00:28:42,970
she’ll see us!

461
00:28:42,970 --> 00:28:44,130
Bonehead!

462
00:28:44,900 --> 00:28:46,180
We?

463
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:47,660
You come for it, right?

464
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:49,970
I only come to challenge Zhou Fei!

465
00:28:51,970 --> 00:28:53,300
Don’t go.

466
00:28:56,060 --> 00:28:58,060
(Lingling Inn)

467
00:29:28,820 --> 00:29:30,900
Who are they?

468
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:33,090
They’re with Four-guardian Mountain.

469
00:29:33,090 --> 00:29:35,420
I met them once.

470
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:37,940
They’re with Tortoise Master.

471
00:29:40,420 --> 00:29:42,940
They look strange.

472
00:29:42,940 --> 00:29:45,210
Why are they wearing the mourning?

473
00:29:46,610 --> 00:29:48,940
I hear Tortoise Master Ding Kui

474
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:51,210
isn’t a good man.

475
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:11,610
Are you from Xingnan Sect?

476
00:30:11,610 --> 00:30:13,850
We have something important to tell you.

477
00:30:13,850 --> 00:30:16,130
Give us the invitation

478
00:30:16,130 --> 00:30:17,420
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

479
00:30:18,780 --> 00:30:21,700
Robbing in the inn in broad daylight?

480
00:30:21,700 --> 00:30:23,090
How lawless you are!

481
00:30:23,940 --> 00:30:25,780
We want the invitation,

482
00:30:25,780 --> 00:30:27,370
just because we don’t like it

483
00:30:27,370 --> 00:30:30,730
when you run errands
for Huo Liantao, the hypocrite.

484
00:30:31,730 --> 00:30:34,730
When he’s holding
the Demon-Extermination Assembly,

485
00:30:34,730 --> 00:30:37,130
you even bring a cart of gifts to him.

486
00:30:38,850 --> 00:30:39,580
Will your cousin

487
00:30:39,580 --> 00:30:41,970
help those people?

488
00:30:41,970 --> 00:30:44,940
She’s here looking for Xie Yun,
instead of fighting.

489
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:46,660
They’re having a dog-fight.

490
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:48,060
Why must she interfere?

491
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:51,210
You want to interfere?

492
00:30:51,210 --> 00:30:52,180
You...!

493
00:30:53,460 --> 00:30:55,580
We’re just passing by

494
00:30:55,580 --> 00:30:58,010
and teasing Huo Liantao’s dogs.

495
00:30:59,130 --> 00:31:00,570
What?

496
00:31:01,490 --> 00:31:03,370
Our sect is famous
for martial arts, too.

497
00:31:03,370 --> 00:31:04,940
Stop slandering us!

498
00:31:05,850 --> 00:31:07,420
Young girl.

499
00:31:07,420 --> 00:31:09,180
Who are you?

500
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:11,210
When Old Master Zhu was in charge,

501
00:31:11,210 --> 00:31:14,460
your family could barely
be a famous sect.

502
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:17,610
Since he was paralyzed in bed,

503
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:20,660
you’ve failed to do martial arts

504
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:23,180
and have even done business for living.

505
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:26,210
How can you still say
you’re martial artists?

506
00:31:26,210 --> 00:31:28,090
Oh, look at the invalid.

507
00:31:28,090 --> 00:31:29,820
He could never practice martial arts.

508
00:31:29,820 --> 00:31:31,900
He’s as weak as a girl.

509
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:33,850
I mean, not even as weak as a girl.

510
00:31:33,850 --> 00:31:36,370
No wonder you must ingratiate yourselves
with Huo Liantao.

511
00:31:36,370 --> 00:31:38,540
Without his help,

512
00:31:38,540 --> 00:31:41,820
your family would have disappeared.

513
00:31:42,730 --> 00:31:43,380
Ying.

514
00:31:47,250 --> 00:31:49,490
I don’t care when you slander me.

515
00:31:49,490 --> 00:31:51,420
But when you slander Junior Master Huo

516
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:53,850
in Lingling Town,

517
00:31:53,850 --> 00:31:55,490
don’t you fear you’ll cause problem?

518
00:31:55,490 --> 00:31:57,180
Problem?

519
00:31:57,180 --> 00:31:59,660
Don’t you know

520
00:31:59,660 --> 00:32:01,370
how he became the master of Huo’s Manor?

521
00:32:01,370 --> 00:32:03,060
Even before

522
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,330
the Demons arrived,

523
00:32:04,330 --> 00:32:07,610
Huo Liantao ran away with fear,

524
00:32:07,610 --> 00:32:10,090
leaving his huge properties behind.

525
00:32:10,090 --> 00:32:13,130
How shameless he is!

526
00:32:13,130 --> 00:32:14,900
And he dares

527
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:18,300
to send out invitations?

528
00:32:18,300 --> 00:32:21,330
You’d better give us the invitation,

529
00:32:21,330 --> 00:32:22,300
so that we can challenge Huo Liantao

530
00:32:22,300 --> 00:32:26,540
on your behalf.

531
00:32:31,780 --> 00:32:34,420
Young man, don’t be nervous.

532
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:36,900
I won’t eat your young master.

533
00:32:40,490 --> 00:32:41,970
Since you’re Junior Master Huo’s enemy，

534
00:32:41,970 --> 00:32:43,460
you can fight with him.

535
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:45,210
We are mere businessmen.

536
00:32:45,210 --> 00:32:46,900
And we haven’t offended you.

537
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:48,420
When you don’t dare
to fight him directly,

538
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:49,460
you give vent on us.

539
00:32:49,460 --> 00:32:50,660
What do you think you’re doing?

540
00:32:50,660 --> 00:32:52,900
Bullying the weak
and being scare of the strong?

541
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:56,460
You think you can bully
whoever you want?

542
00:32:56,460 --> 00:32:58,250
Let me say it again.

543
00:32:58,250 --> 00:33:00,250
Give me the invitation,

544
00:33:00,250 --> 00:33:03,250
and I’ll let you go.

545
00:33:03,250 --> 00:33:05,820
The invitation is for my family.

546
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:06,970
Even if you kill me,

547
00:33:06,970 --> 00:33:08,010
I won’t give it to you

548
00:33:08,010 --> 00:33:09,700
in case you deceive others!

549
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:10,730
Evil!

550
00:33:10,730 --> 00:33:11,940
You defamed my family

551
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:13,610
and hurt our men so brutally!

552
00:33:19,700 --> 00:33:20,940
Mr. Zhu.

553
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:24,130
Which matters more,
your sister or the invitation?

554
00:33:24,130 --> 00:33:26,210
Think carefully about it.

555
00:33:26,210 --> 00:33:27,730
Let go of my sister!

556
