On my way here, I heard a lot

559
00:33:51,130 --> 00:33:52,580
that the Demon-Extermination Assembly

560
00:33:52,580 --> 00:33:54,660
was exactly for treasure-grabbing.

561
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:57,180
Huo Liantao printed the ripple pattern

562
00:33:57,180 --> 00:33:58,460
on the invitations,

563
00:33:58,460 --> 00:34:00,780
calling on people to grab the treasure.

564
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:02,090
How come?

565
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:04,900
How does Huo Liantao
have the ripple pattern?

566
00:34:05,060 --> 00:34:06,780
If he has it,
why doesn’t he keep it to himself?

567
00:34:07,420 --> 00:34:08,330
Cousin.

568
00:34:08,330 --> 00:34:09,940
Then why did those men
with Tortoise Master

569
00:34:09,940 --> 00:34:11,770
snatch the invitation?

570
00:34:11,770 --> 00:34:13,460
Go ask the master of Xingnan Sect

571
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:16,130
if there’s the ripple pattern
on the invitation.

572
00:34:22,500 --> 00:34:24,290
You’re the master of Xingnan Sect?

573
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:27,220
No, no, no.

574
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:29,370
I’m from the Zhu family.

575
00:34:29,370 --> 00:34:30,610
I’m Zhu Chen.

576
00:34:30,610 --> 00:34:32,810
My father is the master of our sect.

577
00:34:32,810 --> 00:34:34,900
He was a great man.

578
00:34:34,900 --> 00:34:37,810
But he suffered a sneak attack
on his way to business.

579
00:34:38,260 --> 00:34:40,220
So far, he’s been paralyzed in bed.

580
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:45,050
So you’re the young master
of Xingnan Sect?

581
00:34:47,090 --> 00:34:49,370
Huo Liantao sent you an invitation?

582
00:34:49,370 --> 00:34:50,180
Yes.

583
00:34:50,330 --> 00:34:51,370
Yes.

584
00:34:52,180 --> 00:34:54,770
I’ve been weak since I was born
and don’t have martial arts.

585
00:34:54,770 --> 00:34:57,610
For my father and sister,
I must reply on Huo’s Manor

586
00:34:57,610 --> 00:34:59,850
and do business within their territory.

587
00:34:59,850 --> 00:35:00,570
This time,

588
00:35:00,570 --> 00:35:03,130
I come to support Master Huo.

589
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:04,810
Oh,

590
00:35:04,810 --> 00:35:07,810
thank you for saving us.

591
00:35:07,810 --> 00:35:10,260
May I know your name?

592
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:12,290
Zhou Fei,
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

593
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:14,220
Li Yan,
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

594
00:35:16,180 --> 00:35:17,530
Don’t be scared.

595
00:35:17,530 --> 00:35:19,420
I just want to have a look.

596
00:35:19,420 --> 00:35:20,810
I won’t snatch your invitation.

597
00:35:21,260 --> 00:35:22,220
It’s okay.

598
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:23,090
Mr. Lin.

599
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:43,060
(From Huo Liantao with Huo’s Manor)

600
00:35:44,050 --> 00:35:45,460
He’s really after this.

601
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:46,460
Who?

602
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:50,700
Thanks.

603
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:52,570
Miss.

604
00:35:52,570 --> 00:35:55,180
Sorry for disturbing your meal.

605
00:35:55,850 --> 00:35:58,020
I’ve prepared some snacks from Jiankang

606
00:35:58,500 --> 00:35:59,610
just to show our gratitude.

607
00:36:00,290 --> 00:36:01,260
No, thanks.

608
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:02,290
I’m not hungry.

609
00:36:03,180 --> 00:36:04,740
I’m hungry.

610
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:06,420
Thank you for this.

611
00:36:09,050 --> 00:36:10,260
Waiter.

612
00:36:10,570 --> 00:36:11,330
Be right there.

613
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:26,050
Mr. Qian Suiyou, why are you here alone?

614
00:36:34,850 --> 00:36:36,570
Madam Nichang?

615
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:40,420
Long time no see. What a coincidence!

616
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,700
It is?

617
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:43,740
We come here for the same purpose,
don’t we?

618
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:45,020
It can’t be a coincidence.

619
00:36:47,980 --> 00:36:49,220
Don’t say it out,

620
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:50,810
or it’ll be boring.

621
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:56,460
I just come to see the fun.

622
00:37:01,090 --> 00:37:04,090
He’s here
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

623
00:37:04,090 --> 00:37:06,500
Can you find him asap?

624
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:08,810
Lately, martial artists from all places
have come into Lingling Town

625
00:37:08,810 --> 00:37:11,290
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

626
00:37:11,290 --> 00:37:13,900
Even if you know he’s also going for it,

627
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:16,220
I’m afraid it’ll take much time

628
00:37:16,220 --> 00:37:18,130
to find him among so many people.

629
00:37:18,130 --> 00:37:20,130
The man you’re after is sly.

630
00:37:20,130 --> 00:37:21,940
He keeps hiding himself from us.

631
00:37:21,940 --> 00:37:24,050
I’ve exhausted my tricks.

632
00:37:25,500 --> 00:37:28,500
-Well...
-Miss, if you’re anxious,

633
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:30,290
I’ll ask our elders

634
00:37:30,290 --> 00:37:31,570
to think of a way

635
00:37:31,570 --> 00:37:33,050
and send more men for help.

636
00:37:33,850 --> 00:37:34,700
Thank you.

637
00:37:49,330 --> 00:37:51,610
How delicious!

638
00:37:57,330 --> 00:37:59,220
Fei, come over!

639
00:37:59,220 --> 00:38:01,660
Famous snacks in Jiankang
are true to their names!

640
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:03,020
Come over. Come.

641
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:07,770
Among all great restaurants,

642
00:38:07,770 --> 00:38:09,050
half are in Jiankang.

643
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:14,130
Miss Zhou, you know this saying.

644
00:38:14,130 --> 00:38:15,850
Have you visited Jiankang before?

645
00:38:16,850 --> 00:38:18,020
When there’s a chance,

646
00:38:18,050 --> 00:38:19,940
I’ll invite you to Jiankang.

647
00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:21,460
Among all great restaurants,

648
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:22,980
half are in Jiankang.

649
00:38:25,050 --> 00:38:26,090
I haven’t gone there before.

650
00:38:27,090 --> 00:38:29,740
I have a friend fastidious about food.

651
00:38:29,740 --> 00:38:31,130
He’s from Jiankang.

652
00:38:32,810 --> 00:38:33,770
Fei.

653
00:38:34,050 --> 00:38:35,900
Do you mean Mr. Xie?

654
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:38,700
Mr. Xie?

655
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:44,090
Focus on your food.

656
00:38:46,980 --> 00:38:48,900
Why are you alone now?

657
00:38:49,610 --> 00:38:51,180
Where is Fei?

658
00:38:52,570 --> 00:38:55,980
I’m used to travelling alone.

659
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:57,460
Well,

660
00:38:58,020 --> 00:39:00,020
it’s troublesome to bring a girl.

661
00:39:00,020 --> 00:39:01,980
Hurting my cool image.

662
00:39:11,090 --> 00:39:12,260
Really?

663
00:39:14,810 --> 00:39:16,130
Denying true thoughts

664
00:39:16,130 --> 00:39:18,330
isn’t a good habit for young men.

665
00:39:18,330 --> 00:39:20,050
You will miss her,

666
00:39:20,050 --> 00:39:21,330
perhaps.

667
00:39:21,330 --> 00:39:23,220
How come?

668
00:39:23,220 --> 00:39:24,700
I’m just busy avoiding her.

669
00:39:24,700 --> 00:39:25,570
Avoiding?

670
00:39:26,900 --> 00:39:28,810
Speaking of avoiding,

671
00:39:28,810 --> 00:39:32,050
you’re avoiding
only when she looks for you.

672
00:39:32,050 --> 00:39:34,090
Are you sure she’s looking for you?

673
00:39:37,980 --> 00:39:39,180
What?

674
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:42,810
You always have a glib tongue.

675
00:39:42,810 --> 00:39:44,260
Now you can’t argue?

676
00:39:48,180 --> 00:39:49,700
Young man.

677
00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:51,740
Don’t deceive yourself.

678
00:39:58,260 --> 00:39:59,660
When we’re fated
to have no happy ending,

679
00:40:01,130 --> 00:40:01,740
what else can I do

680
00:40:02,770 --> 00:40:03,940
except avoiding her?

681
00:40:10,900 --> 00:40:12,020
Madam Nichang.

682
00:40:12,660 --> 00:40:14,610
I’ve got something else to do. See you.

683
00:40:14,610 --> 00:40:17,130
If I have new lyrics,

684
00:40:17,130 --> 00:40:18,700
I’ll go see you in Yuyi Troupe.

685
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:27,020
Qian Suiyou.

686
00:40:29,660 --> 00:40:32,180
Don’t always bother about the ending.

687
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:34,850
The ending you want
may not be what others want.

688
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:37,770
Why don’t you just follow your heart?

689
00:41:02,660 --> 00:41:03,500
Go.

690
00:41:09,610 --> 00:41:12,260
Miss Zhou has also
come to Lingling Town.

691
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:13,330
What a coincidence!

692
00:41:13,330 --> 00:41:14,420
It’s not a coincidence.

693
00:41:15,020 --> 00:41:17,570
All martial artists have come here

694
00:41:17,570 --> 00:41:19,460
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

695
00:41:20,570 --> 00:41:23,220
Our young master also...

696
00:41:23,770 --> 00:41:25,180
You have the nerve to say that?

697
00:41:26,220 --> 00:41:28,900
Unfortunately, Miss Zhou is
also looking for Mr. Xie.

698
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:33,700
Why is Zichen in Lingling Town?

699
00:41:41,570 --> 00:41:43,740
She isn’t staying with him?

700
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:45,700
Since Mr. Xie isn’t with her,

701
00:41:45,700 --> 00:41:47,220
why do you need to meet her?

702
00:41:47,220 --> 00:41:49,130
What if she knows something?

703
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,330
Oh,

704
00:41:52,020 --> 00:41:53,290
when you see her,

705
00:41:53,290 --> 00:41:54,420
show some respect.

706
00:41:55,020 --> 00:41:57,260
If she hadn’t helped us out,

707
00:41:57,420 --> 00:42:00,370
we wouldn’t have run away from Huarong.

708
00:42:00,370 --> 00:42:01,130
Aye.

709
00:42:23,530 --> 00:42:24,660
Who is it?

710
00:42:50,050 --> 00:42:50,850
Xie Yun?

711
00:42:53,570 --> 00:42:54,770
You freaked me out.

712
00:42:56,700 --> 00:42:57,570
Zichen.

713
00:42:57,740 --> 00:42:59,180
I waited for a long time.

714
00:42:59,180 --> 00:43:00,090
I can finally come in,

715
00:43:00,090 --> 00:43:01,420
when Mr. Bai is away.

716
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:03,810
Time is running out. I’ll be brief.

717
00:43:04,850 --> 00:43:06,130
Why must you come in

718
00:43:06,130 --> 00:43:07,660
when Mr. Bai is away?

719
00:43:09,420 --> 00:43:11,610
Because he’s with Route Gang.

720
00:43:11,610 --> 00:43:13,420
He’s looking for me
throughout the town.

721
00:43:13,420 --> 00:43:14,740
If Mr. Bai sees us,

722
00:43:14,740 --> 00:43:16,220
I’ll be biting the hook.

723
00:43:16,660 --> 00:43:18,050
Why are they...

724
00:43:18,420 --> 00:43:20,090
Don’t ask why they’re looking for me.

725
00:43:20,500 --> 00:43:23,330
Tell me. Why do you come here?

726
00:43:23,330 --> 00:43:25,290
Did Huo Liantao invite you?

727
00:43:29,330 --> 00:43:31,050
Not really.

728
00:43:31,050 --> 00:43:33,700
Junior Master Huo is holding
the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

729
00:43:33,700 --> 00:43:36,130
I’d like to take this chance

730
00:43:36,130 --> 00:43:38,050
to learn from Lord Mengchang
in the ancient time

731
00:43:38,050 --> 00:43:40,220
so that I can unite
righteous martial artists

732
00:43:40,220 --> 00:43:41,900
and win their trust.

733
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,610
It won’t do harm, anyway.

734
00:43:45,020 --> 00:43:46,770
There aren’t many righteous men.

735
00:43:46,770 --> 00:43:48,020
Even if there were some,

736
00:43:48,020 --> 00:43:50,180
they wouldn’t come to such an assembly.

737
00:43:50,180 --> 00:43:51,180
Why?

738
00:43:51,180 --> 00:43:52,810
Stop asking why.

739
00:43:53,500 --> 00:43:55,090
There’s much trouble in Lingling Town.

740
00:43:55,090 --> 00:43:56,260
When Mr. Bai comes back,

741
00:43:56,610 --> 00:43:57,660
leave right away.

742
00:43:59,980 --> 00:44:01,260
Why can you come

743
00:44:01,260 --> 00:44:02,530
and why can’t I?

744
00:44:02,530 --> 00:44:02,980
Why...?

745
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:04,290
Stop.

746
00:44:04,290 --> 00:44:06,050
Why do you have so many questions?

747
00:44:06,260 --> 00:44:07,980
Anyway, this is all I can tell you.

748
00:44:09,020 --> 00:44:10,290
I’ll ask no more, then.

749
00:44:13,810 --> 00:44:14,810
Xie Yun.

750
00:44:15,050 --> 00:44:17,330
Why don’t you go with us?

751
00:44:17,330 --> 00:44:18,700
When you and Mr. Bai go with me

752
00:44:18,700 --> 00:44:20,610
and Junior Master Huo is an old friend,

753
00:44:20,610 --> 00:44:21,740
I don’t need to be scared.

754
00:44:21,740 --> 00:44:22,570
Look.

755
00:44:22,850 --> 00:44:24,370
I’ve stayed in your room for a while.

756
00:44:24,370 --> 00:44:26,260
But no men with Mr. Bai have found me.

757
00:44:26,260 --> 00:44:28,260
You really think you’re safe?

758
00:44:29,050 --> 00:44:30,660
Mr. Bai just told me

759
00:44:30,660 --> 00:44:32,900
Miss Zhou was in Lingling Town.

760
00:44:32,900 --> 00:44:33,940
He has gone to pick her up.

761
00:44:33,940 --> 00:44:35,090
When they’re back, I’ll be safe.

762
00:44:35,090 --> 00:44:36,260
What?

763
00:44:36,370 --> 00:44:37,700
Fei has come?

764
00:44:37,700 --> 00:44:38,810
Yeah.

765
00:44:38,810 --> 00:44:39,980
Xie Yun, you know what?

766
00:44:39,980 --> 00:44:41,570
She’s the heir of South Blade.

767
00:44:41,570 --> 00:44:42,700
Mr. Bai said

768
00:44:42,700 --> 00:44:44,050
when we were in Huarong,

769
00:44:44,050 --> 00:44:45,740
Miss Zhou helped us

770
00:44:45,740 --> 00:44:47,090
and held back the Demons.

771
00:44:47,090 --> 00:44:48,420
Otherwise, we wouldn’t have...

772
00:44:51,500 --> 00:44:52,500
Xie Yun?

773
00:44:57,770 --> 00:44:58,810
This way, please.

774
00:44:59,500 --> 00:45:00,700
Elder Bai has come.

775
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:02,260
He said you saved him

776
00:45:02,260 --> 00:45:04,180
and he’d like to visit you personally.

777
00:45:04,180 --> 00:45:05,330
Elder Bai?

778
00:45:13,940 --> 00:45:16,940
Miss Zhou, thank you
for helping us last time.

779
00:45:16,940 --> 00:45:18,290
You’re welcome, Mr. Bai.

780
00:45:18,740 --> 00:45:19,570
I wonder

781
00:45:19,570 --> 00:45:21,500
what you want me for.

782
00:45:22,130 --> 00:45:25,020
I hear you’re looking for Mr. Xie.

783
00:45:25,020 --> 00:45:26,940
Well, we’re looking for him, too.

784
00:45:27,130 --> 00:45:29,770
But he’s too mysterious to be found.

785
00:45:29,770 --> 00:45:31,850
We only know
he has come to Lingling Town.

786
00:45:31,850 --> 00:45:32,660
Yes.

787
00:45:32,660 --> 00:45:35,660
I was just informed

788
00:45:35,660 --> 00:45:38,130
that he would go
to the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

789
00:45:38,660 --> 00:45:39,980
You’re also looking for him?

790
00:45:39,980 --> 00:45:40,610
Yes.

791
00:45:40,610 --> 00:45:42,180
Why do you want him for?

792
00:45:42,980 --> 00:45:44,290
To tell the truth, Miss Zhou,

793
00:45:44,980 --> 00:45:47,810
Prince Zichen heard
of the ripple pattern

794
00:45:47,810 --> 00:45:48,900
and insisted on coming to Lingling Town

795
00:45:48,900 --> 00:45:51,370
for the Demon-Extermination Assembly.

796
00:45:51,850 --> 00:45:53,940
None of us managed to stop him.

797
00:45:53,940 --> 00:45:55,570
We think

798
00:45:55,570 --> 00:45:56,980
if Mr. Xie could help to persuade him,

799
00:45:56,980 --> 00:45:58,260
that would be great.

800
00:46:04,740 --> 00:46:08,250
♪Stars flow like river♪

801
00:46:09,310 --> 00:46:12,910
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

802
00:46:13,480 --> 00:46:17,550
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

803
00:46:17,800 --> 00:46:21,440
♪I will never be alone♪

804
00:46:21,440 --> 00:46:25,560
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

805
00:46:25,980 --> 00:46:30,410
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

806
00:46:31,070 --> 00:46:35,630
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

807
00:46:35,860 --> 00:46:40,490
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

808
00:46:40,680 --> 00:46:44,510
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

809
00:46:44,730 --> 00:46:49,420
♪When I go across the world for you♪

810
00:46:49,680 --> 00:46:53,420
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

811
00:46:53,750 --> 00:46:58,840
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

812
00:46:58,840 --> 00:47:02,780
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

813
00:47:02,780 --> 00:47:07,310
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

814
00:47:07,930 --> 00:47:15,030
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

815
00:47:15,770 --> 00:47:20,400
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
